{"tid":544791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁君彥發信警告民主派　議事規則示威行動涉違法","createTime":"2018-01-30T01:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T03:16:55.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c00e1aa6c67ebd136be332cb4c1ff1e676afdd54","tid":544791,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/092619_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F092619_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=eb62cfac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">泛民議員多次拉布嘗試阻止建制議員通過修改議事規則。</span><br />\n<br />\n立法會行政管理委員會主席梁君彥昨天（29日）去信12名民主派議員，指他們於上月15日立法會審議修改《議事規則》期間，與職員在立法會大樓1樓的示威行動或違反《立法會權力及特權條例》，行管會保留追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n行管會發信警告12名民主派，包括毛孟靜、陳志全、張超雄、郭家麒、葉建源、楊岳橋、尹兆堅、朱凱廸、邵家臻、許智峯、鄺俊宇以及譚文豪。<br />\n<br />\n梁於信件中指，行管會翻看閉路電視片段發現，當晚約6時半立法會進行表決時，10幾名自稱議員職員的人士試圖由1樓升降機大堂進入綠地氈（即會議廳對出）範圍示威，但被保安人員截停，有關職員及後與多名議員在大堂與綠地氈之間的範圍示威，堵塞通道，故行管會認為要向議員及相關職員發警告，指明涉嫌妨礙議員離開會議廳，或違反《立法會權力及特權條例》第382章第19(a)條。<br />\n<br />\n該條文訂明，凡任何人襲擊、妨礙或騷擾任何前往或離開會議廳範圍，或在會議廳範圍內的任何議員，即屬犯罪，可處罰款1萬元及監禁12個月。行管會保留追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/梁君彥發信警告12民主派-議事規則示威行動涉違法/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%E7%99%BC%E4%BF%A1%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A12%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE-%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%2F&d=G%2FjrA1oPeGwhof5TzPmtQozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7f856828\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%E7%99%BC%E4%BF%A1%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A12%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE-%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%2F&h=87718db7\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/梁君彥發信警告12民主派-議事規則示威行動涉違法/</a>"},{"pid":"4d1065c6b49b5f9ca8063901170ee59d96257806","tid":544791,"uid":32588,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:35:53.000Z","msg":"殺左梁君彥咪合法"},{"pid":"2768f20a7fe0dac2de36a909955ad2f8805e5928","tid":544791,"uid":115525,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:36:22.000Z","msg":"比我就唔忍啦<br />\n<br />\n直接叫法官判多過3個月 全部DQ哂佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd838c54baf66402ac40204568e0491849206896","tid":544791,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4d1065c6b49b5f9ca8063901170ee59d96257806","tid":544791,"uid":32588,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:35:53.000Z","msg":"殺左梁君彥咪合法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:51:13.000Z","msg":"不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e57babede559fad7df9ffeb0ec0c131cd6ee23","tid":544791,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2768f20a7fe0dac2de36a909955ad2f8805e5928","tid":544791,"uid":115525,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:36:22.000Z","msg":"比我就唔忍啦<br />\n<br />\n直接叫法官判多過3個月 全部DQ哂佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:53:19.000Z","msg":"唔係唔判呀？"},{"pid":"e0b2ddda9de6b4c6ec1f897b52885a760e0c4276","tid":544791,"uid":32588,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"dd838c54baf66402ac40204568e0491849206896","tid":544791,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4d1065c6b49b5f9ca8063901170ee59d96257806","tid":544791,"uid":32588,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:35:53.000Z","msg":"殺左梁君彥咪合法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:51:13.000Z","msg":"不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:57:43.000Z","msg":"梁振英：以國家的名義殺人不犯法"},{"pid":"d367290968dd0ddfd83c1a7638dab8d67b7e4a2c","t